body_html:
@drpngx I have multiple projects are using different tf built model on Android/iOS mobile device. And I am pre-building the tf and its dependencies lib, before I build my projects(to save compilation time and unifying the tf version for my projects). It was done by gathering(copying) required generated libs and headers files from tf and its dependencies to my projects.

Additional information, my projects are not building with bezel.
